verbose_text: Western blotting and RT-qPCR analyses indicated that total caspase-3 expression was significantly upregulated in the 6OHDA group (1.80 +/-0.20 and 0.28 +/-0.03, respectively) compared to the control group (0.59 +/-0.08 and 0.18 +/-0.02, respectively; P < 0.05; XREF_FIG) and the IA group (0.73 +/-0.03 and 0.24 +/-0.04, respectively; P < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
